column5: Caught a small nurse shark tonight, very cool looking beast.       /media/image_3.jpeg.html][/url]
only her alone can quench that jah thirst!  i didnt know they had nurse sharks up in gods country

cool. now time to catch her momma   enjoy the surf and turf
